# Apple Pear Crisp

Based on [Rustic Apple & Pear Crisp - The Simple Veganista](https://simple-veganista.com/rustic-apple-pear-crisp) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251118014236/https://simple-veganista.com/rustic-apple-pear-crisp/))

